data.name: Fire Fighting
tooltip:
Fire Fighting Skill is based on the character's level. It determines
how quickly they fight fires

how successful they are at putting them
out
and how likely they are to catch on fire themselves!

data.name: Nursing
data.tooltip:
Nursing determines how quickly and successfully this character treats
other characters.

data.name: Logging
data.tooltip:
Logging determines how quickly and successfully the Character can cut
down Foliage - directly contributing to the resource yield.

data.name: Building
tooltip:
Building is very important in Noble Fates. Building determines the
speed
precision

and quality of props that the character builds.
Higher quality props will decay more slowly. In addition

Building
Skill gates access to more advanced recipes.

data.name: Crafting
tooltip:
Crafting is important in Noble Fates. Crafting determines the
speed
precision

and quality of items that the character crafts.
Higher quality leads to higher rarity of items crafted. In addition
crafting Skill gates access to more advanced recipes.

data.name: Guarding
tooltip:
Characters assigned to Guarding will attempt to defend the Kingdom
from threats. They will also handle and intimidate Prisoners and Serfs
as needed.

Guarding is backed by the character's Melee Skill. Melee determines
how often a character attacks
whether their attacks land

and the
amount of their Weapon's damage that is inflicted on target.

data.name: Preaching
data.tooltip:
Preaching determines how quickly and successfully this character influences
other characters.

data.name: Hunting
tooltip:
Hunting determines how quickly and successfully the Character can
Hunt Animals.

Hunting is backed by the Ranged Skill which controls the speed and
accuracy of their ranged shots
which shots they will attempt

and
the amount of their Weapon's damage that is inflicted on target.

data.name: Foraging
data.tooltip:
Foraging determines how quickly and successfully the Character can
Harvest Foliage - directly contributing to the resource yield.

data.name: Farming
data.tooltip:
Farming determines how quickly and successfully the Character can
Plant and Harvest Crops - having a direct impact on their resource
yield.

data.name: Cooking
data.tooltip:
Cooking determines how quickly and successfully the Character can
Cook. Cooking contributes to recipe yield.

data.name: Hauling
tooltip:
Hauling determines how quickly and successfully the Character can
Haul items. In addition

Hauling Skill controls the number of items
that can be carried at the same time.

data.name: Cleaning
data.tooltip:
Cleaning determines how quickly and successfully the Character can
Clean up debris.

data.name: Ranching
data.tooltip:
Ranching determines how quickly and successfully the Character can
interact with animals.

data.name: Mining
data.tooltip:
Mining determines how quickly and successfully the Character can
Mine the terrain.

data.name: Training
data.tooltip: Training determines when characters train their skills when there's no higher priority work.
